game.name: Stink Bomb Madness
game.description: Most people hate their boss and would love to play some pranks on him. Our guy is a scientist in his spare time and he decides to have a little fun creating some original stink bombs, which he can throw on the house of his boss to revenge on the extra work he is always giving him. So play a game of slots to win ingredients, create a stink bomb in the lab, drive to the house and then shoot the bombs by selecting the right angle and power. Have a great time!
